title: Defensive Handgun - Thunder Ranch
description:
Firearms training expert Clint Smith has tutored thousands of students at his legendary Thunder Ranch training facility. Now you can enjoy the best of Clint&#039;s unique teaching style through this new DVD course - all from the comfort of your couch! This two-disk set - filmed at Thunder Ranch in Oregon - is packed full of tips, techniques and Clint&#039;s personal observations about the tactics and gear that work best.

What you&#039;ll get on the Defensive Handgun DVD set:

* Mental Preparation and Logic Lecture. 
* Proper Technique and Application. 
* Loading, Unloading and Malfunction Clearance. 
* Range Demonstration and More!
